  <h1>Project Athena — Payment Portal Modernisation</h1>
  <p><strong>Duration:</strong> [Dates] • <strong>Location:</strong> [Gurgaon / Remote]</p>

  <h3>Objective</h3>
  <p>Migrate legacy .NET payment portal to the cloud-based Hydra platform due to end-of-support, preserving core functionality while upgrading the technology stack.</p>

  <h3>Key responsibilities</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>End-to-end technology upliftment and migration planning</li>
    <li>Data validation and reconciliation to ensure integrity post-migration</li>
    <li>Change management & stakeholder communications</li>
    <li>End-to-end UI UAT and defect triage</li>
    <li>PI planning and design documentation</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Technologies</h3>
  <p>Hydra platform • legacy .NET • SQL • Azure/AWS (if used) • Jira • Confluence • Excel</p>

  <h3>Achievements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Successful migration to Hydra with zero business disruption</li>
    <li>Improved platform maintainability and security posture</li>
  </ul>
